imdb.plot outline: Four young adults bunker down in a warehouse during the robot-zombie apocalypse of 2020. They have a handle on everything until a fifth traveler shows up, uninvited, and with enough issues to fill a bible, or unravel the sanctity of their bonds. Will they be able to accommodate the desperate new refugee or will she become their undoing?
